\f1\b0 \cf2 \strokec2  \cf4 \strokec4 =\cf2 \strokec2  \cf4 \strokec4 "The mammalian brain has very limited ability to regenerate lost\cf2 \strokec2 \
\cf4 \strokec4               neurons and recover function after injury. Promoting the migration\cf2 \strokec2 \
\cf4 \strokec4               of young neurons (neuroblasts) derived from endogenous neural stem\cf2 \strokec2 \
