\cf4 \strokec4               Netrin-1 receptors DCC (deleted in colorectal carcinoma) and UNC5A\cf2 \strokec2 \
\cf4 \strokec4               (uncoordinated-5A) as well as Caspr2 (contactin-associated\cf2 \strokec2 \
\cf4 \strokec4               protein-like 2). Cell-based assays with these antigens showed that\cf2 \strokec2 \
\cf4 \strokec4               among the indicated patients, 9 had antibodies against Netrin-1\cf2 \strokec2 \
