\cf4 \strokec4               Netrin-1 receptor or Caspr2 antibodies predicted thymoma (p <\cf2 \strokec2 \
\cf4 \strokec4               0.05). Coexisting Caspr2 and Netrin-1 receptor antibodies were\cf2 \strokec2 \
